<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><title>eRide Operator Panel - Manual Booking</title><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"><style>body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 15px; background: #f4f4f4; } .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; } input, select, textarea { width: 100%; padding: 12px; margin: 8px 0; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 16px; } button { background: #007bff; color: white; padding: 15px; border: none; width: 100%; font-size: 18px; border-radius: 5px; } .success { color: green; } .error { color: red; } label { font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10px; display: block; }</style></head><body><div class="container"><h2>📞 Phone Booking Entry</h2><p style="color: #666;">For call-in customers from villages</p><% if (success) { %><p class="success">✅ <%= success %></p><% } %><% if (error) { %><p class="error">❌ <%= error %></p><% } %><form method="POST"><label>Customer Name</label><input type="text" name="customerName" required placeholder="Shiv Kumar Sharma"><label>Phone Number (10 digits)</label><input type="tel" name="customerPhone" pattern="[0-9]{10}" required placeholder="9876543210"><label>Pickup Landmark (Village/Area)</label><input type="text" name="pickupLandmark" required placeholder="Bus Stand, Dharmapur"><label>Drop Landmark</label><input type="text" name="dropLandmark" required placeholder="City Hospital, Jaunpur"><label>Pickup Date</label><input type="date" name="pickupDate" required><label>Pickup Time</label><input type="time" name="pickupTime" required><label>Vehicle Type</label><select name="vehicleType" required><option value="auto">Auto Rickshaw</option><option value="hatchback">Hatchback (Indica/WagonR)</option><option value="sedan">Sedan (Dzire/Etios)</option></select><label>Assign Driver (Optional)</label><select name="assignedDriver"><option value="">-- Auto Assign Later --</option><% drivers.forEach(driver => { %><option value="<%= driver._id %>"><%= driver.name %> - <%= driver.vehicleNumber %></option><% }) %></select><label>Special Note</label><textarea name="specialNote" placeholder="Any instructions? Elderly passenger? Luggage?"></textarea><button type="submit">🚕 Confirm Ride & Notify Driver</button></form><a href="/admin/dashboard" style="display: block; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">Back to Dashboard</a></div></body></html>
